description: The initiative, Bybi, began with a focus on community development and social enterprise, evolving into a project centered around urban beekeeping. It aims to foster partnerships between local businesses and community organizations, emphasizing the importance of collaboration and shared responsibility. The initiative seeks to challenge traditional narratives surrounding employment and social development, advocating for a more holistic approach that integrates ecological care and community engagement. By exploring innovative concepts like "honey money," it aims to redefine relationships with resources and promote a sustainable, interconnected community.
name: Bybi
